cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.7)

set(CMAKE_SYSTEM_NAME Generic)
set(CMAKE_TRY_COMPILE_TARGET_TYPE STATIC_LIBRARY)
set(CMAKE_C_COMPILER arm-none-eabi-gcc)
set(CMAKE_CXX_COMPILER arm-none-eabi-g++)
set(CMAKE_ASM_COMPILER arm-none-eabi-gcc)

project(rtdoa_tag VERSION 0.0.0 LANGUAGES C CXX ASM)

SET(CMAKE_C_FLAGS_BACKUP  "${CMAKE_C_FLAGS}")
SET(CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS_BACKUP  "${CMAKE_CXX_FLAGS}")
SET(CMAKE_ASM_FLAGS_BACKUP  "${CMAKE_ASM_FLAGS}")

set_property(SOURCE apps/rtdoa_tag/src/main.c APPEND_STRING
														PROPERTY
														COMPILE_FLAGS
														"-DAPP_NAME=rtdoa_tag -DAPP_rtdoa_tag -DARCH_NAME=cortex_m4 -DARCH_cortex_m4 -DBSP_NAME=dwm1001 -DBSP_dwm1001 -DMYNEWT=1 -DNRF52 -O1 -Wall -Werror -fdata-sections -ffunction-sections -fms-extensions -fno-exceptions -ggdb -mcpu=cortex-m4 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=fpv4-sp-d16 -mthumb -mthumb-interwork -std=gnu99")
# Generating CMakeLists.txt for apps/rtdoa_tag

add_library(apps_rtdoa_tag apps/rtdoa_tag/src/main.c)

							PROPERTIES
							ARCHIVE_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag
							LIBRARY_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag
							RUNTIME_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag)

# Generating code for cmake_rtdoa_tag.elf

file(WRITE bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag/null.c "")
add_executable(cmake_rtdoa_tag.elf bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag/null.c)

target_link_libraries(cmake_rtdoa_tag.elf -Wl,--start-group apps_rtdoa_tag boot_bootutil boot_split crypto_mbedtls crypto_tinycrypt encoding_base64 encoding_cborattr encoding_json encoding_tinycbor fs_fcb hw_bsp_dwm1001 hw_cmsis-core hw_drivers_adc hw_drivers_adc_adc_nrf52 hw_drivers_uart hw_drivers_uart_uart_hal hw_drivers_uwb hw_drivers_uwb_uwb_dw1000 hw_hal hw_mcu_nordic hw_mcu_nordic_nrf52xxx hw_sensor kernel_os lib_bleprph lib_dsp lib_euclid lib_nmgr_uwb lib_rtdoa lib_rtdoa_backhaul lib_rtdoa_tag lib_tdma lib_timescale_timescale_m4_hardfloat lib_uwb_ccp lib_uwb_rng lib_uwb_wcs libc_baselibc mgmt_imgmgr mgmt_mgmt mgmt_newtmgr mgmt_newtmgr_nmgr_os mgmt_newtmgr_transport_ble mgmt_newtmgr_transport_nmgr_shell net_ip_mn_socket nimble nimble_controller nimble_drivers_nrf52 nimble_host nimble_host_services_ans nimble_host_services_gap nimble_host_services_gatt nimble_host_store_config nimble_host_util nimble_transport_ram rtdoa_tag-sysinit-app sys_config sys_console_full sys_flash_map sys_id sys_log_full sys_log_modlog sys_mfg sys_reboot sys_shell sys_stats_full sys_sysinit sys_uwbcfg time_datetime util_cbmem util_crc util_mem util_parse util_rwlock  -Wl,--end-group)
set_property(TARGET cmake_rtdoa_tag.elf APPEND_STRING
														PROPERTY
														COMPILE_FLAGS
														"-DAPP_NAME=rtdoa_tag -DAPP_rtdoa_tag -DARCH_NAME=cortex_m4 -DARCH_cortex_m4 -DBSP_NAME=dwm1001 -DBSP_dwm1001 -DMYNEWT=1 -DNRF52 -O1 -Wall -Werror -fdata-sections -ffunction-sections -fms-extensions -fno-exceptions -ggdb -mcpu=cortex-m4 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=fpv4-sp-d16 -mthumb -mthumb-interwork -std=gnu99")
set_target_properties(cmake_rtdoa_tag.elf
							PROPERTIES
							ARCHIVE_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag
							LIBRARY_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag
							RUNTIME_OUTPUT_DIRECTORY bin/targets/rtdoa_tag/app/apps/rtdoa_tag
							LINK_FLAGS "-Wl,--gc-sections -lgcc -lm -nostartfiles -specs=nosys.specs -static -T/home/kerui/Desktop/UWB_Master/repos/mynewt-dw1000-core/hw/bsp/dwm1001/nrf52xxaa.ld -T/home/kerui/Desktop/UWB_Master/repos/apache-mynewt-core/hw/mcu/nordic/nrf52xxx/nrf52.ld -DAPP_NAME=rtdoa_tag -DAPP_rtdoa_tag -DARCH_NAME=cortex_m4 -DARCH_cortex_m4 -DBSP_NAME=dwm1001 -DBSP_dwm1001 -DMYNEWT=1 -DNRF52 -O1 -Wall -Werror -fdata-sections -ffunction-sections -fms-extensions -fno-exceptions -ggdb -mcpu=cortex-m4 -mfloat-abi=hard -mfpu=fpv4-sp-d16 -mthumb -mthumb-interwork -std=gnu99"
							LINKER_LANGUAGE C)
# Workaround for gcc linker woes
set(CMAKE_C_LINK_EXECUTABLE "${CMAKE_C_LINK_EXECUTABLE} -lgcc -lm")
